               <msContents>
                  <summary>
                     <p>I)መጽሐፈ፡ሰዓታት,Horologium (fols. <locus from="3r" to="79v"/>), incomplete at the end. It resembles in parts the work known as the Horologium (Mäṣḥafä säˁatat) of Giyorgis of Gasǝa (Mäṣḥafä säˁatat zä-Giyorgis)</p>
                     
                     
                     
                  </summary>
                
               </msContents>
